{"tid":891620,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙治羅拔圖爆伊卡迪「房事」","createTime":"2018-11-06T09:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:54:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c59cd1d3026936dca8ebe538cf2c0a967e134e3f","tid":891620,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c2a7298f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育 &middot; 435人追蹤<br />\n10 小時前<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c2a7298f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】美斯在周二歐聯傷癒復出，右閘沙治羅拔圖認為這位球王養傷令球隊變得更強；他更大爆國際米蘭射手莫路伊卡迪的「房事」。<br />\n<br />\n沙治羅拔圖指：伊卡迪效力巴塞青訓時，跟沙治羅拔圖是同房。 沙治羅拔圖表示：「我們一起住了數年，我最記得的是他用玻璃箱養了一隻蜥蜴！」"},{"pid":"fb1e24486e2c77ff59ba3550a98cd876d9f38a21","tid":891620,"uid":44285,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"死廢閘咁多嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27291155e3882b2a4b77afc0853e62797205e02","tid":891620,"uid":25831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b6140e15e5ca948437576188d51fee2f4e1b79","tid":891620,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"樓上全部基佬"},{"pid":"bd4d129773fafbb04e09ede48819f149ed03762f","tid":891620,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1e24486e2c77ff59ba3550a98cd876d9f38a21","tid":891620,"uid":44285,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"死廢閘咁多嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"飲醉？"},{"pid":"ef62290591e850019ef77b3a26e5e9f2bec6ec